/* magical objects */
The large stone tablet(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/obj/tablet) which is
part of the tablet quest has magical properties that allows it to have
a light value of 2.

-Antharanos-

The sparkling red gem(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/obj/srgem) which can
be found hidden in the moss of the troglodyte complex, located in the
dark dominion(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/underdark/u19b) has magical
properties that give it a light value of 1.

-Antharanos-

The flying carpet (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/desert/carpet/carpet) is
the carpet magically enchanted by Duthrala, the Bedellin witch, to
ferry travellers from the nomad camp in Kalad to the border between
Kalad and Cirath.

-Antharanos-

   The gem of light, gem of darkness and bag of holding are all magical
items sold by the merchant in the bazaar of Undraeth. The two gems
emit light and darkness to 1 lvl, respectively. The bag is simply a
standard sack with a bit more room for items. The file names are:
Gem of Light (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/obj/gem_light)
Gem of Darkness (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/obj/gem_dark)
Bag of Holding (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/obj/bag_holding)

-Antharanos-
